%% HelixOS — task state machine

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NEW: task_create
    NEW --> READY: inserted into run queue
    READY --> RUNNING: pick_next selects
    RUNNING --> READY: scheduler_tick preempts
    RUNNING --> SLEEPING: task_sleep_ms(N)
    SLEEPING --> READY: task_wake_due(now ≥ wake_tick)
    RUNNING --> ZOMBIE: task_exit()
    ZOMBIE --> [*]: (not reaped in v0.1)

    note right of READY
        On the run queue.
        scheduler picks the next READY task in RR order.
    end note

    note right of SLEEPING
        Not eligible until wake_tick.
        Wake signal: PIT tick reaching deadline.
    end note

    note right of ZOMBIE
        Exited but PCB lives on.
        v0.2 will add waitpid/reaper.
    end note
